description:
TimeM: This table stores metadata about time-series measurements from Ericsson radio access network equipment, including timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and data version information.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the measurement.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the measurement was taken.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant cell identifier (possibly an alternative identifier).
- Id3:  An arbitrary identifier (purpose unclear from the data).
- Id4: An arbitrary identifier (purpose unclear from the data).
- vsDataType: Type of data stored (here, time-series measurement metadata).
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
- TimeM.timeMId: Unique identifier for the measurement record.
